description:
Growe welcomes those who are excited to:

- Prepare a strategic monthly calendar tailored for Casino and Sports customers;
- Use analytics to drive CRM decisions and planning;
- Conduct weekly analysis on campaign performance and profitability;
- Analyze player behaviors to create targeted segmentations and personalized offers aligned with playing styles;
- Plan, execute, and optimize daily campaigns focused on: player upselling, retention, reactivation;
- Collaborate with content, design, and product teams to create engaging and relevant promotions;
- Manage multi-channel communications via: Email, SMS, push notifications, In-app messages, events & promotions;
- Identify key Sports and Casino events to align with targeted promotions;
- Ensure consistent, compelling, and timely communication around special events and offers;
- Track and report on key CRM metrics, including: retention rate, reactivation rate, churn rate, monthly pulsation flows, ARPU (Average Revenue Per User), campaign conversion rates (acceptance, usage, wagered %), communication metrics (Open Rate, Click-Through Rate, Conversion Rate, Delivery Rate);
- Conduct A/B testing and apply hypothesis-driven analysis to optimize CRM performance;
- Use insights to drive continuous improvement and decision-making.

We need your professional experience:

- 2+ years of experience in a CRM/Retention/Marketing role;
- Experience with the iGaming industry (will be a plus);
- Experience managing VIP segments and executing high-value retention strategies;
- Proficiency in CRM tools, marketing automation platforms, and performance tracking tools;
- A good understanding of player behavior is a strong advantage;
- An Upper-intermediate level of English (written and spoken).

We appreciate if you have those personal features:

- Strong analytical and data interpretation skills with the ability to make strategic decisions based on data;
- Comfortable working under pressure and managing multiple deadlines simultaneously;
- Strong communication and presentation skills with the ability to create and deliver compelling reports and proposals.

We are seeking those who align with our core values:

- GROWE TOGETHER: Our team is our main asset. We work together and support each other to achieve our common goals;
- DRIVE RESULT OVER PROCESS: We set ambitious, clear, measurable goals in line with our strategy and driving Growe to success.<br/><br/>Please mention the word **CHEERY** and tag RMzguNjguMTM0LjE5NA== when applying to show you read the job post completely (#RMzguNjguMTM0LjE5NA==). This is a beta feature to avoid spam applicants. Companies can search these words to find applicants that read this and see they're human.
